item.title: CVE-2024-49340|2024-10-16T14:11:54.598Z -- ibm -- watson%20studio%20local
item.description: IBM Watson Studio Local 1.2.3 is vulnerable to cross-site request forgery which could allow an attacker to execute malicious and unauthorized actions transmitted from a user that the website trusts.
